      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-4">Throughput depends on product mix, destination count, and induct rate. See <a href="/resources/conveyor-cost-guide/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">conveyor cost guide</a> for pricing factors.</p>
